TEXT.S: Valau Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Cwosisyang ka alang Valau. 69 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 273 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 99% niqan 271 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 1% niqan 2 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Bunun 93%, Amis 2%, Tayal 1%, Paiwan 1%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq 1%, ni rahuq na o 2%.
